description:
Use this environment as a backup to open Napari applications that require NapaTrackMater by cloning it and making one for yourself using this command: 

 &nbsp; 

 conda create --name new_env_name --clone /path/to/myenvfolder/ 

 &nbsp; 

 After that you can update the NapaTrackMater and vollseg-napari-trackmate package and they should always work in this environment.

